    /**
     * @dev Exchanges RWD tokens on Tether tokens with discount
     * @param user The address of the user who is exchanging tokens
     * @param amount The amount of RWD tokens to exchange
     * @param deadline The deadline by which the permit must be obtained
     * @param v The v component of the permission signature.
     * @param r The r component of the permission signature.
     * @param s The s component of the permission signature.
